      "text": "私達とファンが繋がった思い出なんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "is a memory of our connection with fans.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.0000180643,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4133.3331267999965
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "この手紙は……沖縄で、一緒に釣りをした人から……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This letter… is from the man we went fishing with in Okinawa…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.9946645025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-szk006.m4a",
      "text": "あの時行った釣り場が、大変なことになってるって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It says the fishing spot we went to has become a big deal…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.766684731,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そういえばネットニュースで見たわ。あの堤防に",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think I saw it on the internet news. Apparently‚ that breakwater",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.2636211637,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2403_01_05-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "サニピのファンが連日詰めかけているそうね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "has been packed with Sunny Peace fans every day.",
